            Why Toxicological Safety Services Are Essential
          </h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray max-w-none">
            <p>
              Indivirtus provides specialized toxicological and safety documentation services to support pharmaceutical
              manufacturing and cleaning validation. These services are critical for ensuring regulatory compliance,
              mitigating risks of cross-contamination, protecting personnel from exposure to hazardous substances, and
              minimizing environmental hazards.
            </p>
            <p>
              By offering end-to-end solutions, including ADE/PDE/OEL & OEB calculations, Safety Assessment Reports
              (SAR) for finished formulations, and expertly prepared MSDS/SDS documents, Indivirtus helps pharmaceutical
              manufacturers and CROs meet stringent global standards. These services are vital for GMP-compliant
              operations, facility design, and regulatory audits, ensuring product safety and workplace health.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

